<DOCNO>WT13-B02-58</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA020-000213-B024-102</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.context.org:80/ICLIB/IC35/Fisk.htm 204.94.52.15 19970107103633 text/html 5119
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
