<H1><CENTER>Bamberton Update</CENTER>
</H1>
<H3><BR>
February 1996</H3>
<BR>
From Guy Dauncey: &quot;The project is currently undergoing a very slow
and thorough process of<BR>
environmental assessment which will take until 1998, as a condition of final
zoning approval. No residential settlement is expected until the year 2000.
Further updates will be posted here once a year.&quot;<BR>
