<H1 align=center>Welcome To GVRD On-Line</H1>



<P align=center>

We have developed this site to give the community greater access to the GVRD<BR>

 and its services. This site is here to assist you whether you're researching, 

 browsing, exploring, looking for entertainment or information.</P>



<P align=center>

<A HREF="go/new.html">What's New; Bright Ideas On Site</A><BR>

