<HEAD>
<TITLE>Working with You
</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<body bgcolor=#FFFFFF text=#000000>
<CENTER><A HREF="../../index.html"><IMG SRC="../medarch/home/head6.gif" BORDER=0></A>

<H1>Working with You: <BR>
Issues, Plans and Projects</H1></CENTER>
<P> <A NAME="vision">In</A> 1990, the Greater Vancouver Regional District Board adopted the 
<CITE>Creating Our Future</CITE> vision:

<P><P><strong><blockquote>"Greater Vancouver can become the first urban region in the world to
combine in one place the things to which humanity aspires on a global basis: 
a place where human activities enhance rather than degrade the natural 
environment, where the quality of the built environment approaches that 
of the natural setting, where the diversity of origins and religions is 
a source of social strength rather than strife, where people control the 
destiny of their community, and where the basics of food, clothing, 
shelter, security and useful activity are accessible to all."</blockquote></strong>
<P ALIGN=center>
<IMG  SRC="../medarch/work/kids.gif" ALT="49k Image of Children 
at play.">
<P> 
The purpose of the <A HREF="futur.html"><B>Livable Region Strategic Plan</B></A> is to help 
realize this vision through Greater Vancouver's land use and transportation 
development.
</EM>
<P><A NAME="menu"></A>
The following sections examine the GVRD issues, plans and projects 
that affect all of us in this region.
<p><UL><LI>
<A HREF="air.html">Let's Clear the Air</A>
<P><LI>
<A HREF="solid.html">Waste Reduction</A>
<P><LI>
<A HREF="drain.html">Wastewater</A>
<P><LI>
<A HREF="water.html">Drinking Water</A>
<P><LI>
<A HREF="../todo/legacy.html">Lower Mainland Nature Legacy</A>
<P><LI>
<A HREF="tax.html">GVRD Tax Dollars</A>
</UL><P><HR>
<P>
GVRD's <A HREF="../../info/bro/cdrom.html"><CITE>Creating Our Future</CITE> CD-ROM</A> 
contains three environmental simulation games to
help you learn about choices that will improve <B>air quality</B>, <B>water</B> and <B>waste</B>.
</P>
<HR>
<A HREF="../../index.html"><IMG SRC="../../go/
medarch/home/smhome.gif" HSPACE=15 BORDER=0></A>
<BR>
[<A HREF="../../index.html">GVRD Home</A>]
