<HTML>

<HEAD>
<TITLE>Departments and Committees
</TITLE>

</HEAD><body bgcolor=#FFFFFF text=#000000>


<CENTER><A HREF="../../index.html"><IMG SRC="../medarch/home/head6.gif" BORDER=0></A></CENTER>


<H1>Departments and Committees; <BR>
Our Mandates and Services</H1>


 

<UL>
<LI><A HREF="depts.html#depart">GVRD Departments</A> 
<LI><A HREF="../../board/bro/commite.html">GVRD Committees</A> 
<LI><A HREF="../../board/bro/bord.html">GVRD Board of Directors</A> 
<LI><A HREF="#member">GVRD Member Municipalities</A>
</UL>

<HR>
<H3>Overview</H3>

The Greater Vancouver Regional District is a partnership of the 20 municipalities and
two electoral areas that make up the metropolitan area of Greater Vancouver. One
Fraser Valley municipality (Abbotsford) outside the GVRD boundaries also
participates in its parks service.
<P>
The role of the Regional District is to deliver to the area's 1.8 million people - 
half the population of British Columbia - essential services that are regional 
rather than local in nature.
<P>
These services are provided on a regional basis for reasons of economy,
effectiveness and fairness. Yet the system is structured so that each member
municipality maintains its local autonomy. 
<P> 
The regional district concept was established by the Provincial Government in 1965; 
the first meeting of the GVRD's Board of Directors was on July 12, 1967.
<P>
There are 29 regional districts in B.C., covering virtually the entire
province.
<P>

<STRONG>
<A NAME="member">GVRD MEMBERS</A><BR> </STRONG>
<UL>
<LI> Village of Anmore
<LI> <A HREF="../../board/members/belc.html">Village of Belcarra </A>
<LI> <A HREF="../../board/members/bby.html">City of Burnaby </A>
<LI> <A HREF="../../board/members/coq.html">City of Coquitlam </A>
<LI> <A HREF="../../board/members/delta.html">District of Delta </A>
<LI> Electoral Area A (University Endowment Lands) 
<LI> Electoral Area C (Bowen Is., Barnston Is., Howe Sound, Indian Arm) 
<LI> <A HREF="../../board/members/langeyc.html">City of Langley </A>
<LI> <A HREF="../../board/members/langeyt.html">Township of Langley </A>
<LI> Village of Lions Bay, 
<LI> <A HREF="../../board/members/mridge.html">District of Maple Ridge </A>
<LI> <A HREF="../../board/members/newwest.html">City of New Westminster </A>
<LI> <A HREF="../../board/members/nvanc.html">City of North Vancouver </A>
<LI> <A HREF="../../board/members/nvand.html">District of North Vancouver </A>
<LI> <A HREF="../../board/members/pittm.html">District of Pitt Meadows </A>
<LI> <A HREF="../../board/members/ptcoq.html">City of Port Coquitlam </A>
<LI> <A HREF="../../board/members/moody.html">City of Port Moody </A>
<LI> <A HREF="../../board/members/rchmd.html">City of Richmond </A>
<LI> <A HREF="../../board/members/surrey.html">City of Surrey </A>
<LI> <A HREF="../../board/members/vanc.html">City of Vancouver </A>
<LI> <A HREF="../../board/members/wvanc.html">District of West Vancouver </A>
<LI> <A HREF="../../board/members/wrock.html">City of White Rock</A>
</UL>
<P>The <A HREF="../../board/members/abbots.html">City of Abbotsford</A> participates in
the provision  of parks services and has representation on the <A HREF="../../board/bro/bord.html">
Board of Directors</A>.<BR>
<HR>
<P>
<H3><A NAME="depart">GVRD Departments</A></H3>
<P>
To carry out its functions the GVRD is organized by departments reflecting
administrative efficiency, program delivery and legal authority.
<P>
The GVRD is comprised of 12 major departments. Of the 12 departments ,
seven (Water, Sewerage and Drainage, Solid Waste, Air Quality, Housing, Hospitals and Regional Parks)
are operational (functional), three (Finance and Administration, Communications and
Education and the Secretary's Office) provide support services while Personnel and
Labour Relations and Strategic Planning contain elements of both.
<P>
<LI><A HREF="../../air/bro/airdept.html">Air Quality Department</A>
<LI><A HREF="../../info/bro/cedept.html">Communications and Education
Department</A> 
<LI><A HREF="../../finance/bro/findept.html">Finance, Administration and Properties
Department</A> 
<LI><A HREF="../../hospitals/bro/hspdept.html">Hospital Planning and
Development Department</A> 
<LI><A HREF="../../housing/bro/hosdept.html">Housing Department</A>
<LI><A HREF="../../personnel/bro/perdept.html">Personnel and Labour Relations
Department</A> 
<LI><A HREF="../../parks/bro/prkdept.html">Regional Parks Department</A>
<LI><A HREF="../../sewers/bro/sddept.html">Sewerage and Drainage Department</A>
<LI><A HREF="../../waste/bro/swdept.html">Solid Waste Department</A>
<LI><A HREF="../../planning/bro/stpdept.html">Strategic Planning Department</A>
<LI><A HREF="../../water/bro/watdept.html">Water and Construction Department</A>
</UL><P>




[<A HREF="../../index.html">GVRD Home</A>]
