<CENTER><H1>GVRD ARCHIVES</H1></CENTER>

	 	

<CENTER><IMG ALIGN=center SRC="../medarch/home/arch.gif" ALT="20K

Image of Archives Button"></CENTER>



<CENTER><H2>YOUR WEALTH OF INFORMATION</H2></CENTER>







<P>This is the major warehouse for GVRD's electronic information.  If you

are looking for GVRD items to inspect or download onto your computer, 

this is the right place to look.</P>

	 

<HR>

	 

<H3>CATEGORIES</H3>

<UL>

	 <LI>Agendas<BR>

		- plans for upcoming committee and board meetings



	 <LI>Committee Minutes<BR>

	 	- minute by minute details

	 	

	 <LI><A HREF="library.html">Library (GVRD)</A><BR>

	 	- listing of services, types of resources and hours of operation



	 <LI>Maps<BR>

	 	- views to review

	 

	 <LI><A HREF="newsrel.html">News Releases</A><BR>

	 	- flash backs on the news

	 	

	 <LI>Photos<BR>

	 	- snapshots on history

	 	

	 <LI>Policy Papers<BR>

	 	- focusing GVRD procedures	

	 	

	 <LI>Reports<BR>

		<A HREF="keyfacts.html">

		<IMG SRC="../medarch/arch/kficon.gif" border=0 align=middle> Greater Vancouver Key Facts 

		<FONT size=-1> (A Statistical Profile of Greater Vancouver)</FONT></A><BR>

        

		<A HREF="/waste/bro/swasses.html">

		<IMG SRC="../medarch/arch/recycon.gif" border=0 align=middle> Waste Assessment Guide for the Workplace</A><BR>

		

		<A HREF="aqar.html">

		<IMG SRC="../medarch/arch/aqicon.gif" border=0 align=middle> Ambient Air Quality Annual Report</A><BR>



	 <LI><A HREF="econind.html">Economic Indicators</A><BR>

	    - monthly statistics on GVRD's economic status

</UL>	 

<BR>

You may also find items within the main body of this site.  For an overview, 

try the <A HREF="../aindex.html">Alphabetical Index</A>.<BR>



