<H1>Website Search</H1>

<P><CENTER><H3>GVRD website search has a search feature, to help<BR>
you find what you need quickly. <BR> 
</H3></CENTER></P>

<P><CENTER><A HREF="#SEARCH">
<IMG SRC="../medarch/home/search.gif" width=109 height=70 BORDER=0></A><BR>
</P align=center><HR></CENTER>

<H4>Searching</H4>
GVRD website search will get you where you want to be.
Simply type in a word or phrase, select keyword or phrase search, 
and you will be given a list of found items to choose from. With <EM>keyword</EM>
search, each word you enter is searched for independently.  With <EM>phrase</EM>
search the the words you enter are used as the phrase to search for.

<FORM method=post action="http://www.gvrd.bc.ca/cgi/search1.cgi">
<P>Keyword<input type=radio name="Phrase" value="false"> 
Phrase<input type=radio name="Phrase" value="true" checked>
<input name="Search" size=30>
<input type="submit" value="Search">  
<input type="reset" value="Clear">
<input name="Scope" value="/go/aindex.htm*" type=hidden>
</P><A NAME="SEARCH">
</FORM>
<BR><BR>Alternatively you can use the 
<A HREF="http://www.gvrd.bc.ca/go/aindex.html">A-Z index</A>
<HR>
[<A HREF="http://www.gvrd.bc.ca/index.html">GVRD Home</A>]</P>
<BR><ADDRESS>For further information or feedback, please email us at <A HREF="mailto:webmaster@gvrd.bc.ca">webmaster@gvrd.bc.ca</A></ADDRESS></BODY>

