<H1>Waste Reduction</H1>
<P>Garbage! Sooner or later just about everything we produce as a society 
ends up as some form of waste. Despite the Canadian public's concern for 
the environment, Canadians are among the most wasteful people in the world.
<P> <IMG SRC="../medarch/waste/lgrecy.gif" ALIGN=RIGHT VSPACE=50
HSPACE=40 ALT="Image of Solid Waste icon">

<H2><A NAME="menu">Solid Waste</A></H2>
