<HEAD>
<TITLE>Wastewater
</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<body bgcolor=#FFFFFF text=#000000>
<CENTER><A HREF=../../index.html><IMG SRC="../medarch/home/head6.gif" BORDER=0></A></CENTER>

<H1>Wastewater System</H1>
<P>
Water covers more than 70 per cent of the globe's surface but only three per cent is fresh water.
This  makes fresh water one of our most precious resources. We depend on it for survival.
<P>
In using fresh water, we sometimes pollute it. Since water must be returned to the 
rivers and sea, we must first remove the pollutants. If we don't, we will end up 
with an unhealthy environment.
<P> <IMG SRC="../medarch/sewer/lgliqu.gif" ALIGN=RIGHT HSPACE=80 VSPACE=16>
This is why wastewater treatment plants are so important. They remove many of the 
pollutants in the water so we can continue to enjoy a clean, healthy environment. 



<H2><A NAME="menu">Wastewater System</A></H2>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="../../sewers/bro/wwover.html">Overview of Wastewater System</A>
