<DOCOLDNO>IA049-000848-B010-277</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.gvrd.bc.ca:80/waste/bro/swgvrdc.html 204.191.162.48 19970119215704 text/html 4370
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sun, 19 Jan 1997 21:56:54 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5b7
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Sat, 07 Oct 1995 01:01:09 GMT
