<DOCNO>WT13-B02-180</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA049-000848-B008-75</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.gvrd.bc.ca:80/waste/bro/swusing.html 204.191.162.48 19970119214807 text/html 4918
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sun, 19 Jan 1997 21:48:02 GMT
