<strong>Advancing Understanding and Predictions of Climate Variability</strong>
<p>
<em><strong>The mission of 
CDC is to identify the nature
and causes for climate variations on time scales
ranging from a month to centuries.  The 
goal of this work is to develop the ability to
predict important climate variations on these
time scales.</strong></em>
