<head>
<title>
Cooperative Ocean-Atmosphere Research Data Service
</title>
</head>
<body>
<center>
<img alt="Cooperative Ocean-Atmosphere Research Data Service" src="title.gif"><br>
<a href="http://www.cdc.noaa.gov/cgi-bin/imagemap/coop-logo">
<img alt="JISAO/UW/CDC/CIRES/FERRET/TOGA-TAO/PMEL/GCPS/NCDC/NOAA" 
src="location.gif" ismap></a>
</center>
<hr size=4>
<br>
<IMG alt="O" SRC="http://www.cdc.noaa.gov/cdc_images/blueball.gif">
<strong>Our primary <a href="purpose.shtml">purpose:</a> 
to provide access to climatological data.
<blockquote>

<IMG alt="O" SRC="http://www.cdc.noaa.gov/cdc_images/blueball.gif">
Do a 
<a href="http://www.cdc.noaa.gov/cgi-bin/COOPSearch.pl?state=2&location=CDC&location=ferret&location=NCDC&location=JISAO">general</a>
or
<a href="http://www.cdc.noaa.gov/cgi-bin/COOPSearch.pl?state=3&location=CDC&location=ferret&location=NCDC&location=JISAO">guided</a>
search of our data holdings. <br>

<!--IMG alt="O" SRC="http://www.cdc.noaa.gov/cdc_images/blueball.gif"-->
<!--a href="visualize.html">Visualize or acquire</a> a data (sub)set.-->
<br>
</blockquote>
</strong>
