<DOCNO>WT13-B02-207</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA002-000022-B043-75</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cdc.noaa.gov:80/cdc/overview/extreme/slide2.html 128.138.218.238 19961231223333 text/html 5414
