<img
align=bottom border=0
alt=""
src="images/new.gif">

<a
href="products.html">Latest real-time images</a>.

<hr>

<p>The Satellite Climate Research Group uses data from various 
environmental satellites in studies of seasonal to interannual climate 
variability.  Topic areas of interest include studies of air-sea
interaction including transfers of heat, momentum, and water; studies 
of the global hydrological cycle including water vapor and 
precipitation; and studies of the Earth's radiation budget.
<p>

<img alt="" src="images/go_back.gif"><a href="http://www.cdc.noaa.gov/">Back to CDC home</a>

