<li>
Ferraro, R. R., E. A. Smith, W. Berg, and G. J. Huffman, 1996: A review
     of screening techniques for passive microwave precipitation retrieval
     algorithms, <I> J. Atm. Sciences</I>, accepted pending revisions.<P>

<li>
Greenwald, T.J., G.L. Stephens, T.H. Vonder Haar, and D.L. Jackson,
1993:  A physical retrieval of cloud liquid water over the global
oceans using SSM/I observations. <I>J. Geophys. Res.</I>, <B>98</B>, 18,
471-18,488. <a href="/~dlj/dljref.html#5">Abstract available</a><P>

<li>
Jackson, D.L., 1992:  On the role of SSM/I derived precipitable water
over the globe and tropical pacific.  M.S. Thesis, Colorado State
University, 112 pp. <a href="/~dlj/dljref.html#6">Abstract available</a><P>

<li>
Jackson, D.L., and G.L. Stephens, 1995:  A study of SSM/I derived
columnar water vapor over the global oceans. <I> J. Climate </I>,
<B>8</B>, 2025-2038. <a href="/~dlj/dljref.html#3">Abstract available.</a><P>

<li>
Stephens, G. L., D. L. Jackson, and J. J. Bates, 1994: A
comparison of SSM/I and TOVS colunm water vapor data over the global
oceans.  <I>Meteorology and Atmospheric Physics.</I>, <B>54</B>,
183-201. <a href="/~bates/batesref.html#7">Abstract available.</a>
<p>

<li>
Stephens, G.L., D.L. Jackson, and J.J. Bates, 1994:  A comparison of
SSM/I and TOVS column water vapor data over the global oceans. <I>
Meteorol. Atmos. Phys.</I>, <B>54</B>, 183-201. <a href="/~dlj/dljref.html#4">Abstract available.</a><P>

<li>
Stephens, G.L., D.L. Jackson, and I. Wittmeyer, 1996: Global
observations of upper-tropospheric water vapor derived from TOVS
radiance data. <I>J. Climate</I>, <B>9</B>, 305-326. <a href="/~dlj/dljref.html#2">Abstract available.</a><P>

<li>
Sun, Guowu and Q. Ye, 1996: A Study on the Variation of Drought Periods
 	Occurring in Northwest China and Other Africa-Asia Contiental Regions.
	Acta Meteorologica Sinica, 10, 473-484.<P>

<li>
Tjemkes, S.A., G.L. Stephens, and D.L. Jackson, 1991:  Spacebourne
observation of columnar water vapor: SSMI observations and algorithm.
