<H2>NCEP Reanalysis Atlas Updates</H2>
</center>
<dl>
<dt><b>12-30-96:</b><dd>Added geopotential height and air temperature eof's for northern hemisphere. Added precipitable water.
<dt><b>12-10-96:</b><dd>Added tropospheric temperature and pressure variables.
<dt><b>10-08-96:</b><dd>Added diurnal cycle of several variables including surface u,v, pressure, and air temperature. Also added diurnal cycle of geopotential height for all levels. Diurnal cycle was calculated for 4 separate months.

<dt><b>09-17-96:</b><dd>Redid u and v wind monthly mean (individual years, long term mean and interannual standard deviation) files because of correction to daily wind files by NCEP <a href="http://www.cdc.noaa.gov/cdc/reanalysis/problems.shtml">(details)</a>
</dl>
