<title>
NCEP/NCAR Reanalysis Status
</title>
</head>

<body>
<h1>NCEP/NCAR Reanalysis Status</h1>
<h2>(updated: Monday, 18-Nov-96 08:14:13 MST)</h2>

<hr>

<h2>At CDC:</h2>
We have finished processing 1979-1995
for the pressure level, tropopause, surface, surface gauss, other gauss
 and spectral data.  
All of these data are now available on-line.
<p>
We have received 1973-1978 from NCEP.  These data have not been processed
or put on-line.  We do not currently have storage space for these new data.
<p>
For details of about outstanding problems see the 
<a href="http://www.cdc.noaa.gov/cdc/reanalysis/problems.shtml"> 
problem list.</a>
<hr>


For more information contact the CDC Data Management Group:
<p>
Climate Diagnostics Center, U.S. Dept. of Commerce NOAA, 
Code R/E/CD, 325 Broadway, Boulder, CO 80303
<p>
<address>cdcdata@cdc.noaa.gov</address>

