<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>CDC Map Room Climate Products</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<center>
<a href="http://www.cdc.noaa.gov">
<img alt="Climate Diagnostics Center" src="http://www.cdc.noaa.gov/cdc_images/banner.gif"></a>
</center>
<B>
<P>
<CENTER><H1><A name="top">CDC Map Room Climate Products</a></H1></CENTER>
<HR SIZE=3>
The CDC Map Room Climate Page is designed for easy access
to products useful for monitoring weekly to annual fluctuations
of global and regional climate.  There are three primary data 
sources for these products: 1) final atmospheric analyses from
the National Meteorological Center (NMC), 2) outgoing longwave
radiation and other satellite data from NESDIS and 3) weekly
SST and ocean analyses from the Coupled Model Project at NMC.
The graphic output from these data are currently being produced 
with the use of the NCAR Graphics, IDL, and GEMPAK software 
packages.  A paragraph descibing the scientific framework for 
the project can be accessed by 
<a href="/~map/maproom/text/framework.shtml">
clicking here</a>.
<P>
<HR SIZE=3>
<H2><A name="main_menu">Main Menu</a></H2>
<UL>
<LI> <a href="/~map/maproom/text/climate_pages/aam.shtml">
     Atmospheric Angular Momentum</a>
<LI> <a href="/~map/maproom/text/climate_pages/glbwind.shtml">
     Global Windfield Mode</a>
<LI> <a href="/~map/maproom/text/climate_pages/sst.shtml">
      Sea Surface Temperature</a>
<LI> <a href="/~map/maproom/text/climate_pages/olr.shtml">
     Outgoing Longwave Radiation (OLR)</a>
<LI> <a href="/~climsat/products.html">
     Satellite Climate Products</a>
<LI> <a href="/~map/maproom/text/climate_pages/glbcir.shtml">
     Global Circulation and Anomalies</a>
<LI> <a href="/~map/maproom/text/climate_pages/storm.shtml">
     Storm Tracks and other High Frequencies</a>
<LI> <a href="/~map/maproom/text/climate_pages/ocean.shtml">
     Weekly Ocean Analyses</a>
<HR SIZE=1>
<I>
<LI> <a href="/~cas/boulder.html">
      Boulder Area Climate and Weather Data</a>
<LI> <a href="/~map/maproom/text/weather_products.shtml">
      CDC Map Room Weather Products </a>
</I>
<HR SIZE=1>
<p>
<LI><a href="/~map/maproom/index.shtml"> 
    <I> Return to CDC Map Room Top-Level Page </I> </a>

</UL> 

